00:02:00.773 --> 00:02:01.893
I advise you to be sensible.

00:02:02.090 --> 00:02:03.533
Pay up obediently and avoid trouble.

00:02:04.572 --> 00:02:05.212
Otherwise,

00:02:05.812 --> 00:02:07.573
