to accuse you.

00:03:06.092 --> 00:03:07.972
Of course I won't kill him now.

00:03:08.532 --> 00:03:11.212
Liu Qinghe placed Tang Run at my side

00:03:11.293 --> 00:03:12.013
to test me.

00:03:12.412 --> 00:03:13.613
Then I'll play along

00:03:14.132 --> 00:03:15.092
and turn it against him.

00:03:15.573 --> 00:03:16.893
Make Tang Run work for me

00:03:17.412 --> 00:03:19.773
to uncover Liu Qinghe's secrets.

00:03:21.212 --> 00:03:21.652
Good.

00:03:22.013 --> 00:03:23.453
I can get the key tonight.

00:03:25.173 --> 00:03:26.252
